quran[88]{c,v,t}:
  38,1,S/C/SAD and the Koran (owner) of the reminder/remembrance
  38,2,But those who disbelieved (are) in glory/might/power and defiance/animosity
  38,3,"How many from (a) people of one era/generation We destroyed from before them? So they called: \"And it is not the time, time for escape (expression)"
  38,4,"And they were wondering/astonished/surprised that (a) warner/giver of notice came to them from them, and the disbelievers said: \"That (is a) liar/denier/falsifier, (a) magician/sorcerer"
  38,5,Did he make the gods one god? That (E) that (is an) astounding/surprising thing (E)
  38,6,"And the assembly/nobles set out that: \"Walk and be patient on your gods, that (E) (is) a thing (E) is being wanted/intended"
  38,7,"We did not hear/listen with that in the religion/faith the last, that (E) that is except creations/inventions"
  38,8,"Is the reminder/remembrance descended on (to) him from between us? But they are in doubt/suspicion from My remembrance/reminder, but till now they did not taste/experience My torture"
  38,9,"Or at them (is) your Lord`s safes/storages (of) mercy, the glorious/mighty the grantor/presenter"
  38,10,Or for them (is) the skies`/space`s and the earth`s/Planet Earth`s and what (is) between them (B)`s ownership/kingdom ? So they should ascend/climb in the reasons/connections
  38,11,Soldiers/warriors from the groups/parties at that place and time (are) defeated
  38,12,"Noah`s, and Aad`s, and Pharaoh`s nation, (owner) of the stakes/pegs/nails denied/falsified before them"
  38,13,"And Thamud and Lot`s nation, and owners/company (of) the thicket/dense tangled trees, those are the groups/parties"
  38,14,"That (E) each/all except they did (without exception) lied/denied/falsified the messengers, so (they) deserved My punishment"
  38,15,"And those do not look/see/watch except (for) one loud strong cry/torture raid, (there is) nothing from (a) recovery/awakening for it"
  38,16,"And they said: \"Our Lord hurry/hasten/speed for us our share/prize voucher/accounting book before the Account Day/Resurrection Day"
  38,17,"Be patient on what they say, and mention/remember Our worshipper/slave David, (owner) of the power/strength/force, that he truly is repentant/returning"
  38,18,"That We, We manipulated/subjugated the mountains with him, they praise/glorify at the evening/first darkness and the sun rise"
  38,19,"And the birds gathered, each/all for him (are) returning"
  38,20,"And We strengthened/supported his ownership/kingdom, and We gave/brought him the wisdom and judgment/decision (of) the speech/address/conversation"
  38,21,"Did information/news (of) the disputers/adversaries/arguers come to you, when they climbed/scaled the center of the house/center of the assembly"
  38,22,"When they entered on (to) David, so He was frightened/terrified from them, they said: \"Do not fear (we are) two disputers/adversaries/arguers, some of us oppressed/transgressed on some (over each other), so judge/rule between us with the truth/just , and do not be unjust , and guide us to the road`s/way`s middle/straightness"
  38,23,"That, this (is) my brother for him (are) nine and ninety ewes/female sheep, and for me (is) one ewe/female sheep. So he said: `Let me sponsor/maintain it.` And he overwhelmed me in the speech/conversation"
  38,24,"He (David) said: \"He had (E) caused injustice to you/oppressed you with requesting your ewe/female sheep to his ewes/female sheep, and that many from the associates/company some of them oppress/transgress (E) on some (each other) except those who believed and made/did the correct/righteous deeds, and little/few what they are.\" And David doubted/suspected that We tested him so he asked for forgiveness (from) his Lord, and he fell down bowing, and He repented/obeyed"
  38,25,"So We forgave for him that, and that for him at Us (is) an advancement/rank/degree (E) and (a) good/beautiful return"
  38,26,"You David, that We made/put you (as) a caliph/leader in the land/Earth , so judge/rule between the people with the truth/just , and do not follow the self attraction for desire , so it misguides you from God`s way/path , that those who misguide from God`s way/path, for them (is) a strong (severe) torture because (of) what they forgot the Account Day/Resurrection Day"
  38,27,"And We did not create the skies/space and the earth/Planet Earth and what (is) between them (B) wastefully/falsely , that is those who disbelieved`s doubt/suspicion, so calamity/scandal to those who disbelieved from the fire"
  38,28,"Or We make/put those who believed and made/did the correct/righteous deeds as/like the corrupting in the earth/Planet Earth, or We make/put the fearing and obeying as/like the debauchers/corrupters"
  38,29,"A Book We descended it to you blessed, (so) they consider (E) its verses/ evidences and (to the owner`s) of the pure minds/hearts to mention/ remember"
  38,30,"And We granted to David Soliman, blessed/praised the slave/servant that he truly is repentant"
  38,31,When the horses standing on three legs and the edge of the fourth hoof touching the ground (of) the beautiful necks were displayed/exhibited/showed on (to) him at the evening/first darkness
  38,32,"He said: \"That I , I loved/liked love (of) the good/honour/wealth on (over) mentioning/remembering my Lord, until it became hidden/concealed (disappeared) at the divider/protection"
  38,33,"Return it on (to) me, so he started and continued with the shins/legs, and the necks rubbing/petting/anointing"
  38,34,And We had (E) tested/charmed Soliman and We threw on his throne/seat a body then he repented
  38,35,"He said: \"My Lord forgive for me, and grant/present for me an ownership/kingdom (that) should not be to anyone from after me, that You, You are the grantor/presenter"
  38,36,"So We manipulated/subjugated for him the wind/breeze it flows/passes with his order/command, soft/gentle where/when it struck/marked"
  38,37,And the devils all/each (is a) builder/constructor and diver
  38,38,And others tied to each other in the shackles/chairs
  38,39,"That (is) Our granting , so bless (do kind acts) and hold/seize without counting"
  38,40,And that (E) for him at Us (is) an approachment/degree/rank (E) and a good/beautiful return
  38,41,"And remember/mention Our worshipper/slave Job, when he called/cried (to) his Lord: \"That I, the devil touched me with hardship/fatigue/disease and torture"
  38,42,"Run/move/push with your foot, that (is a) cool/cold washing place/water, and a drink"
  38,43,"And We granted/presented to him his family and equal to them with them, mercy from Us and a reminder/remembrance to (owners) of the pure minds/hearts"
  38,44,"And take with your hand a handful of grass/a handful, so strike/beat with it, and do not break oath, that We, We found him patient blessed/praised the slave/servant , that he truly is repentant"
  38,45,"And remember/mention Our worshippers/slaves Abraham, and Isaac, and Jacob, (owners of) the hands, and the eyesights/knowledge"
  38,46,That We made them become faithful/clear/purified with clear/pure reminder/remembrance (of) the House/Home
  38,47,"And they, they are at Us from (E) the chosen/purified, the good/honoured"
  38,48,"And remember/mention, Ishmael, and Elija (owner) of the cloth saddle , and each/all (are) from the good/honoured"
  38,49,"That is a reminder, and that truly to the fearing and obeying (is a) good/beautiful (E) return"
  38,50,"Treed gardens/paradises (as) eternal residences, the doors/entrances (are) opened for them"
  38,51,"Leaning/reclining in it, they call in it with much/many fruits, and a drink"
  38,52,"And at them (are) the eyes`/eye lids` confining/limiting/restricting, same age/not aging"
  38,53,That (is) what you are being promised to the Account Day/Resurrection Day
  38,54,"That (E) this (is) Our provision (E), (there is) nothing from (a) depletion from it"
  38,55,"This, and that truly to the tyrannizing/arrogant (is a) bad/evil (E) return"
  38,56,"Hell they roast/suffer (from) it, so how bad (are) the beds (destination)"
  38,57,"This, so they will taste/experience it hot/cold water , and cold/decayed/rotten"
  38,58,And other/another from its likeness/similarity spouses
  38,59,"This (is a) group/crowd bursting/plunging with you, (there is) no welcome with (for) them, that they are, they are entering/suffering the fire"
  38,60,"They said: \"But you are (there is) no welcome with (for) you, you advanced/introduced it for us.\" So how bad (is) the settlement/decision"
  38,61,"They said: \"Our Lord who advanced/introduced this for us, so increase him (with) a double torture in the fire"
  38,62,"And they said: \"Why (is it) for us, we do not see men, we were, we count them from the bad/evil/harmful"
  38,63,We took them (by) mocking/ridiculing or the eyesights/knowledge deviated/turned away from them
  38,64,"That truly that (is) true/fact (E) , the fire`s people dispute/ controvert/argue (among them selves)"
  38,65,"Say: \"Truly I am (a) warner/giver of notice, and (there is) none from a God, except God the one, the defeator/conqueror"
  38,66,"The skies`/space`s and the earth`s/Planet Earth`s Lord, and what (is) between them (B), the glorious/mighty ,the forgiving often/forgiver"
  38,67,"Say: \"Is it (a) great news/information"
  38,68,You are from it objecting/opposing
  38,69,"(There) was not from knowledge to me with the group/assembly/nobles, the highest/mightiest when they dispute/controvert/argue"
  38,70,That (it) is (only) inspired/transmitted to me except that I am a clear/evident warner/giver of notice
  38,71,"When your Lord said to the angels: \"That I am creating a human from mud/clay"
  38,72,"So if I straightened him, and I blew in him from My Soul/Spirit , so fall/come to him prostrating"
  38,73,"So the angels prostrated all of them, all/all together"
  38,74,"Except Satan he became arrogant, and was/is from the disbelievers"
  38,75,"He said: \"You Satan , what prevented/prohibited you that you prostrate to what I created with My hands, did you become arrogant, or you were from the high and mighty"
  38,76,"He said: \"I am better than him, You created me from fire and You created him from mud/clay"
  38,77,"He said: \"So get out/emerge from it, so that you are cursed/expelled"
  38,78,And that (E) on you (is) My curse/torture/expulsion to the Judgment Day/Resurrection Day
  38,79,"He said: \"My Lord so give me time/delay me to a day/time they be sent/resurrected/revived"
  38,80,"He said: \"So that you are from the given time/delayed"
  38,81,"To day/time (of) the time, the known"
  38,82,"He said: \"So with Your glory/might , I will misguide/lure them (E) all/all together"
  38,83,"Except Your worshippers/slaves from them, the faithful/devoted"
  38,84,"He said: So the truth and the truth I say"
  38,85,I will fill (E) Hell from you and from who followed you from them all/all together
  38,86,"Say: \"I do not ask/question you on it from a reward/wage/fee, and I am not from the pretentious/meddling"
  38,87,That (E) it is except a reminder/remembrance to the creations all together/(universes)
  38,88,And you will know (E) its news/information after a time/period of time